{"tid":601670,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"銀公：本港銀行體系有充夠資金去應付資金流出","createTime":"2018-03-22T11:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T13:19:55.000Z","uid":70274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c403f2a66f36f57f58eb9381def187c65057a265","tid":601670,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"infocast<br />\n<br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 銀公署理主席梁兆基表示，對於港元近來疲弱，主要由於自2008年美國量化寬鬆，帶動本港資金流入1萬億港元，而本港銀行體系結餘充裕。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，環球退出量化寬鬆，或會影響港匯，若港匯觸及7.85弱方保證兑換水平，而金管局出手就會賣美元，買港元，這是一個聯繫匯率之下的恒常的機制，即使港匯觸及7.85水平，不代表有龐大資金流出。<br />\n<br />\n他補充，本港持有4萬億元高流動資產，而外匯基金佔其中的3萬億元，相信本港銀行體系有充夠資金去應付資金流出，對本港來説完全不是任何憂慮。(EC)"},{"pid":"bc7c0882b2ecc7eebc168a08bbe96a9b7654ca2a","tid":601670,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:41:51.000Z","msg":"又唔加"},{"pid":"f41c14d2c277625e2df00b8f61e34edd826d1157","tid":601670,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"係呀 冇資金流出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478249d1ca9d24ea1b4a0c3596d5b46c16abe685","tid":601670,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"挑金管局機"},{"pid":"0a6645656f8e79461447795e36ab460d9061f15e","tid":601670,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:46:17.000Z","msg":"支那由14年中到17年1月，燒左成一萬億美元外匯儲備<br />\n真係走資起上黎，一萬億港幣燒得幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cad17234e9dd2dd33b3e8f04077d6338662560","tid":601670,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靠波叔同班國際炒家鬥會點?"},{"pid":"ca810b3d186db26961fa4d9f452629291bbd34f0","tid":601670,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a6645656f8e79461447795e36ab460d9061f15e",